# SuperRobots

SuperRobots is a web app for showcasing your robot team!

## Features

- Team member profiles
- Robot gallery
- Team achievements
- Contact form

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:
    ```
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/superrobots.git
    ```
2. Install dependencies:
    ```
    npm install
    ```
3. Start the development server:
    ```
    npm start
    ```

## Folder Structure

- `/src` - Source code
- `/public` - Static assets

## Tech Stack

- React (frontend)
- Node.js/Express (backend)
- MongoDB (database)

